# Test des endpoints ServiceType après migration

### 1. Login pour obtenir un JWT token
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@test.com",
  "password": "TempPass123!"
}

### 2. List ServiceTypes (POST /list pour filtrage avancé)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/service-types/list
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "page": 1,
  "limit": 10,
  "sortBy": "name",
  "sortOrder": "asc"
}

### 3. Create ServiceType
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/service-types
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "businessId": "{{business_id}}",
  "name": "Consultation Générale",
  "code": "CONS_GEN",
  "description": "Consultation médicale générale",
  "isActive": true
}

### 4. Get ServiceType by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/service-types/{{service_type_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

### 5. Update ServiceType
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/v1/service-types/{{service_type_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Consultation Spécialisée",
  "description": "Consultation médicale spécialisée mise à jour"
}

### 6. Delete ServiceType
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/v1/service-types/{{service_type_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}